data.name: Yune, the Ambusher
data.notes: "Yune, the Ambusher" is a rare spawn at the north west shore of Seabirds Beak which is the beach at the south end of Sylvalum that sticks out into the ocean. Either reload the area with fast travel/return to Skell or move in and out of the spawn area until the game loads Yune.
